<header>
    <h4>CALLING FOR A GREATER TRANSPARENCY, SUSTAINIBILITY AND ETHICS IN THE FASHION INDUSTRY</h4>
</header>
<div class="wrapper">
    <form method="POST">
        <h1>because there is no planet b</h1>
        <h2>fill out the form to be part of our movement</h2>
        <input type="text" class="inputfields" name ="firstname" placeholder="first name"></input>
        <input type="text" class="inputfields" name ="lastname" placeholder="last name"></input>
        <input type="email" class="inputfields" name ="email" placeholder="email"></input>
        <input type="password" class="inputfields" name="password" autocomplete="off" placeholder="password"></input>
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
